A=Amos Rastport
R=6
While Mouse Key=0
A$="" : Ink 2
For T=0 To 30
A$=A$+"O"
Add R,6
Wb Gfx Centre A$,160,R To A
Wait 2
Next T
A$="" : Ink 3
For T=30 To 0 Step -1
A$=A$+"O"
Add R,-6
Wb Gfx Centre A$,160,R To A
Wait 2
Next T
Wend 
